reviewText: It is relatively hard to find Lash La Rue movies at all, much less in a nice collection like this.  He is one of my childhood heroes, along with the Lone Ranger and Tom Mix.  If you are a fan of Lash, you should get this collection.

While a bit formulaic, the entertainment value is there for fans of the "B" western.  What Lash lacked in acting chops, he made up for with lots of action. A big dose of Saturday afternoon double bill satisfaction!
